宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，总投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2500</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元，占地面积</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">66</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亩，可供</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">100</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">户村民居住的渡普镇烟墩社区，举行了盛大的奠基典礼。县领导余珂、李鹏谋、魏朝东、贺隆君、戴书萍、魏萍出席了奠基典礼。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">继去年投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1300</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">多万建成了顾氏新村供</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">24</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">户村民免费居住后，湖北嘉晟集团董事长顾枫决定投入重资再建烟墩社区。该项目以建设新型农村为目标，采取项目扶持一点、企业投入一点、入住村民自筹一点的方式，运用土地整治项目资金进行土地平整、产业建设和基础设施配套，湖北净宝农业发展有限责任公司出资具体承担建设任务，进行统一规划、统一设计、统一施工、统一建设，建成后统一交付村民入住。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">该项目总占地面积</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">66</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亩，建筑面积</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1.8</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万平米，总投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2500</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元，可供</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">100</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">户村民居住。房屋采用白墙青瓦的徽派建筑风格，户型为独立二层楼房，不仅有架空层和后院，还设有独立厨房、贮藏室，院内可栽花种菜、养猪养鸡。社区配套建设绿化带、休闲广场、幼儿园、医务室、商店等公共场所和设施。该项目计划今年底交付村民使用。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县长余珂在奠基典礼上致辞，他要求渡普镇及县直有关部门通力协助、密切配合、搞好服务，及时解决项目推进过程中的困难和问题，为项目建设提供贴心服务；同时希望嘉晟集团坚持高标准规划、高水平建设、高质量管理，把烟墩社区建成我县最具代表性、标志性的新农村社区之一，建成农民群众满意的居住场所。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">&ldquo;我是从渡普镇净堡村走出去的农民儿子，支持家乡建设、报答家乡父老是我从小的愿望和追求，我将继续克服困难、不断前行，尽自己的力量为父老乡亲办实事！&rdquo;湖北嘉晟集团董事长顾枫在奠基典礼上说道。</span></font></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-01-12/525518951e79367b16be86c309604a8d.jpg\\\\\" /></span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">烟墩社区规划图</span></font></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1247','6','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-01-12/29af435eed7ae94d36bcfeb0ed31a30a.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">座谈会现场<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">11</span>日下午，县委常委、宣传部长刘合权，副县长魏萍分赴北街、东街社区，检查督办冬季人口和计划生育工作。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">在听取了北街社区人口和计划生育优质服务情况汇报、查阅台账资料后，刘合权强调，春节前后是流动人员返乡的高峰期，也是抓好计生工作的最关键时期。鱼岳镇及社区要集中时间、集中人力抓计生；要进一步明确责任，集中开展好孕情监测、&ldquo;三查四术&rdquo;工作；要加强与各包保科局、驻社区单位的联系，及时反应情况、上报信息，再加措施、再加力度，力争把人口和计生工作抓出成效。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">在东街社区人口与计生工作座谈会上，魏萍认真听取该社区&ldquo;单位负责、以房管人&rdquo;工作落实情况，仔细核查在孕人数、流动人口办证、政策外生育社会抚养费征收等信息。她要求社区要抢抓当前有利时机，大力开展摸底排查，包保单位要积极出资出力，搞好协调配合，共同推动人口和计生工作再上新台阶。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">鱼岳镇及相关社区、县计生局主要负责人参加会议。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1249','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">13</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，副县长魏萍率县计生工作专班赴高铁岭镇检查督办计生工作。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">魏萍一行通过听取汇报、查阅台帐资料等方式，详细了解了该镇计生工作开展情况。魏萍指出，春节前后是抢抓计划生育工作的关键时期，高铁岭镇务必迅速落实专职领导、专班人员、专项经费，集中精力打好计划生育&ldquo;突击战&rdquo;。以控制违法生育为中心，切实做好&ldquo;三查四术&rdquo;和孕情监测工作，加强督促检查及宣传教育，稳定低生育水平，控制人口出生性别比。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">魏萍强调，计生工作要切实做到&ldquo;真、严、勤&rdquo;。即各项统计数据和台帐资料要真实可靠，实事求是；检查督办要严格，对工作措施不力、推卸责任、弄虚作假的责任人要严格追究；督办要勤，每周至少进行两次巡回督查，勤走访群众和育龄妇女，做到常抓不懈。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
